text: cng klaw theid(muhammad) wa “phwk than cng thangan theid læ wxallxh ca thrng hen kar ngan khxng phwk than læa rx sul khxng phraxngkh læa br rda mux mi nk ca hen dwy læa phwk than ca thuk na klab pi yang phra phuthrng rx br nı sing renlab læa sing peidphey læw phraxngkh ca thrng cæng kæa phwk than nı sing thi phwk than tha wi”
